The GENMOT program allows you to investigate the  07
dynamics of any system with up to three degrees   08
of freedom.                                       09
                                                  10
The differential equations describing the system  11
must be entered as a Pascal Procedure using the   12
examples included with the software as a guide.   13
Once the program has been compiled, the program   14
allows you to investigate the dynamics            15
graphically and numerically.                      16
