ParametersHelp
             PARAMETERS                           01
                                                  02
This option allows you to change the initial      03
conditions, force parameters, and numerical       04
parameters.  When changing the force parameters   05
or the numerical parameters you have the option   06
of resetting the dynamical variables back to the  07
initial conditions or continuing from the current 08
values.  Thus, you can change the force in the    09
middle of the simulation.  RACETRACK.PAS shows    10
how you can set up the keyboard to provide        11
direct user control over parameters.              12
